text: Yakup is a Turkish given name for males and is a cognate of Jacob and James. People named Yakup include: * Yakup Ağa (fl. 1462), Ottoman cavalry knight * Yakup Bugun (born 1987), Turkish footballer * Yakup Gör (born 1988), Turkish sport wrestler * Yakup Kadri Karaosmanoğlu (1889–1974), Turkish novelist * Yakup Kılıç (born 1986), Turkish boxer * , Turkish journalist * Yakup Satar (1898–2008), last Turkish veteran of the First World War * Yakup Sertkaya (born 1978), Turkish footballer * Yakup Şener (born 1990), Turkish amateur boxer * Yakup Şevki Subaşı (1876–1939), general of the Ottoman Army and the Turkish Army ==See also== * Yakub * Jacob (name) Category:Turkish masculine given names
title: Yakup
